_header: God that madest all thing of nought
_description: A Prayer to God the Father — two six-line stanzas

BLAdd39574.First Lines:
GOd þat madist al þing of nouȝtAnd with þi
                    precious blood us bouȝt…
BLAdd39574.Last Lines:
…Swete Ihesu us ruweþ sooreMercy for þin holy
                    name
